rive<br />\ngoogle apps for work要成120 /yr 仲要5條友夾<br />\namazon drive 無限先59.99 / yr<br />\n不過聽講Amazon個速要睇你好唔好彩"},{"pid":"922b89f2ab3ddc683b2a92a57a361fe20483bc70","tid":81734,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Amazon</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有用amazon，但係冇得search file真係好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n裝linux<br />\n<br />\nlinux既acd_cli用fuse令amazon cloud drive變到幾個hdd咁，d片就咁用vlc開都得<br />\n<br />\n不過睇怕用緊windows既大家望完linux呢隻字之後會無視呢個回覆，心入面諗1000個理由出黎keep住用windows。acd個official gui唔洗用大家都知係垃圾，大家最後都係會嫌呢樣野而唔去用acd架啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0a24cf53fe95576009beff692705a8369e55bf","tid":81734,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>google drive係無限咩？</blockquote><br />\nGoogle apps for work有5條友夾先有無限. 如果唔係都係得1TB<br />\n就咁去google drive最多30TB仲要貴.<br />\n要平既話一定係用 amazon drive<br />\ngoogle apps for work要成120 /yr 仲要5條友夾<br />\namazon drive 無限先59.99 / yr<br />\n不過聽講Amazon個速要睇你好唔好彩</blockquote><br />\n26gb big hero six可以流暢睇既程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a031f7bea5588669f6be1848d6647291c2e2bf4","tid":81734,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://megabackup.com/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegabackup.com%2F%20&d=fKS%2B8ftiISyyt3LDjTGZuAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6a2b1283\" target=\"_blank\">https://megabackup.com/ </a> 好似好平"},{"pid":"b39900e80c56e2f9534dec65f3e05e1aca597a81","tid":81734,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"講容量+可靠Amazon真係冇得輸<br />\n不過速度方面我4 thread total都係3-15MB/s左右<br />\n<br />\n想快就一定Google drive<br />\nupload輕鬆上90-100MB/s<br />\ndownload唔知佢係咪有限速就三四十咁<br />\n<br />\nGoogle教育plan係無限容量<br />\n不過如果你唔係學生/阿Sir/admin既<br />\n就睇吓你過唔過